OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,7,FStaying largely dry overnight with
OL,8,Fclear periods although patchy low
OL,9,Fcloud may develop, with a chance of
OL,10,Fisolated fog patches. Staying rather
OL,11,Fwarm and humid in coastal regions.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA locally grey and misty
OL,14,Fstart, but soon becoming widely bright
OL,15,Fwith sunny periods, these increasingly
OL,16,Fprolonged through the afternoon. A
OL,17,Fwarm day albeit cooler and breezier on
OL,18,Fsome coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
